data.description: Welcome to 235 Forest Parkway, Alabaster, AL 35007 – a move-in-ready haven on 3.5 acres. This charming home features a new covered back porch, ideal for relaxation. The kitchen boasts brand-new appliances, blending style and function. Outside, discover two large storage buildings offering versatility. With ample land and modern amenities, this residence is ready for you. Seize the opportunity for comfortable living and outdoor space. Schedule a showing today!
